<!doctype html><html lang="ko"><head><meta charset="utf-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1"><title>업체관리</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/style.css"><style>.wrap{max-width:1100px;margin:30px auto;padding:0 18px}.box{border:1px solid #29324f;border-radius:18px;background:#101525;padding:22px;margin-bottom:18px}.form{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:10px}.form input,.form select,.form textarea{height:42px;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid #29324f;background:#070b15;color:#fff;padding:0 12px}.form textarea{grid-column:1/3;height:120px;padding:12px}.form button{grid-column:1/3;height:46px;border:0;border-radius:999px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#ff3fb4,#10d9ff);color:#fff;font-weight:900}@media(max-width:800px){.form{grid-template-columns:1fr}.form textarea,.form button{grid-column:1}}
.paybox{border:1px solid #10d9ff;border-radius:14px;background:#06111c;padding:14px;margin:10px 0}
.paybox b{color:#10d9ff}.paybox code{display:block;word-break:break-all;background:#030712;border:1px solid #29324f;border-radius:10px;padding:10px;margin-top:8px}
</style></head><body><header class="top"><a class="brand" href="/">서비스 디렉터리</a><nav><a href="/">사이트</a><a href="/logout">로그아웃</a></nav></header><main class="wrap"><section class="box"><h2>업체관리</h2><% if(vendor){%><div class="box" style="background:#070b15"><h3>업체 통계</h3><p>조회수 <b><%=vendor.views||0%></b> · 후기 <b><%=stats?.review_count||0%></b>개 · 평균평점 <b><%=stats?.avg_rating||"-"%></b> · 찜 <b><%=stats?.favorite_count||0%></b>개 · 신고 <b><%=stats?.report_count||0%></b>건</p><p>상품등급: <b><%=vendor.membership_type==="recommended"?"추천등록":"일반등록"%></b> · 등록만기일: <b><%=vendor.expire_at||"-"%></b> · 배너: <b><%=vendor.banner_active?"활성":"-"%></b> <%=vendor.banner_until||""%></p></div><p><b><%=vendor.name%></b> / <%=vendor.region%> / <%=vendor.category%></p><p>수정 내용은 바로 반영되지 않고 관리자 승인 후 반영됩니다.</p><form method="post" action="/vendor-dashboard/update-request" enctype="multipart/form-data" class="form"><input name="name" value="<%=vendor.name||''%>" placeholder="업체명"><select name="category"><% settings.categories.forEach(x=>{%><option <%=vendor.category===x?'selected':''%>><%=x%></option><%})%></select><select name="region"><% settings.regions.forEach(x=>{%><option <%=vendor.region===x?'selected':''%>><%=x%></option><%})%></select><input name="phone" value="<%=vendor.phone||''%>" placeholder="연락처"><input name="kakao_url" value="<%=vendor.kakao_url||''%>" placeholder="카카오톡 링크"><input name="business_hours" value="<%=vendor.business_hours||''%>" placeholder="영업시간"><input name="tags" value="<%=vendor.tags||''%>" placeholder="태그"><input type="file" name="image" accept="image/*"><textarea name="description" placeholder="업체소개"><%=vendor.description||''%></textarea><button>수정요청 보내기</button></form><%}else{%><p>연결된 업체가 없습니다.</p><%}%></section><section class="box"><h3>프리미엄배너 신청</h3><p>프리미엄배너 승인 시 추천업체로 자동 승격되며, 기존 등록 만기일에 맞춰 배너도 함께 종료됩니다.</p><div class="paybox"><b>배너 가격</b><p><%=Number(settings.raw.banner_price_krw||0).toLocaleString()%>원 / <%=((Number(settings.raw.banner_price_krw||0))/(Number(settings.raw.usdt_krw_rate||1400))).toFixed(2)%> USDT</p><p>네트워크: <%=settings.raw.usdt_network||"TRC20"%></p><code><%=settings.raw.usdt_address||"관리자가 입금주소를 설정하지 않았습니다."%></code></div><form method="post" action="/vendor-dashboard/banner-request" enctype="multipart/form-data" class="form"><input name="title" placeholder="배너 제목" required><input name="subtitle" placeholder="배너 부제목"><input name="link_url" placeholder="연결 링크 URL"><input type="file" name="image" accept="image/*" required><button>배너 신청하기</button></form></section><section class="box"><h3>광고 연장 신청</h3><div class="paybox"><b>광고 가격</b><p>30일 <%=Number(settings.raw.ad_price_krw_30||0).toLocaleString()%>원 / <%=((Number(settings.raw.ad_price_krw_30||0))/(Number(settings.raw.usdt_krw_rate||1400))).toFixed(2)%> USDT</p><p>60일 <%=Number(settings.raw.ad_price_krw_60||0).toLocaleString()%>원 / <%=((Number(settings.raw.ad_price_krw_60||0))/(Number(settings.raw.usdt_krw_rate||1400))).toFixed(2)%> USDT</p><p>90일 <%=Number(settings.raw.ad_price_krw_90||0).toLocaleString()%>원 / <%=((Number(settings.raw.ad_price_krw_90||0))/(Number(settings.raw.usdt_krw_rate||1400))).toFixed(2)%> USDT</p><p>네트워크: <%=settings.raw.usdt_network||"TRC20"%></p><code><%=settings.raw.usdt_address||"관리자가 입금주소를 설정하지 않았습니다."%></code></div><form method="post" action="/vendor-dashboard/ad-request" class="form"><select name="plan"><option value="premium">프리미엄 광고</option><option value="recommend">추천업체 광고</option></select><select name="period"><option value="30">30일</option><option value="60">60일</option><option value="90">90일</option></select><textarea name="content" placeholder="요청사항"></textarea><button>광고 연장 신청하기</button></form></section><section class="box"><h3>배너/광고 신청 내역</h3><table><tr><th>구분</th><th>내용</th><th>상태</th><th>메모</th></tr><% (bannerRequests||[]).forEach(r=>{%><tr><td>배너</td><td><%=r.title%><br><small><%=Number(r.krw_price||0).toLocaleString()%>원 / <%=r.usdt_amount||0%> USDT</small></td><td><%=r.status==='approved'?'승인':r.status==='rejected'?'반려':r.payment_status==='waiting'?'입금확인대기':'입금대기'%></td><td><%=r.admin_memo||'-'%><% if(r.status==='new'&&r.payment_status!=='waiting'){%><form method="post" action="/vendor-dashboard/banner-request/<%=r.id%>/paid"><button>입금완료</button></form><%}%></td></tr><%})%><% (adRequests||[]).forEach(r=>{%><tr><td>광고연장</td><td><%=r.plan%> / <%=r.period%>일<br><small><%=Number(r.krw_price||0).toLocaleString()%>원 / <%=r.usdt_amount||0%> USDT</small></td><td><%=r.status==='approved'?'승인':r.status==='rejected'?'반려':r.payment_status==='waiting'?'입금확인대기':'입금대기'%></td><td><%=r.admin_memo||'-'%><% if(r.status==='new'&&r.payment_status!=='waiting'){%><form method="post" action="/vendor-dashboard/ad-request/<%=r.id%>/paid"><button>입금완료</button></form><%}%></td></tr><%})%></table></section><section class="box"><h3>수정요청 내역</h3><table><tr><th>ID</th><th>업체명</th><th>상태</th><th>관리자 메모</th></tr><% requests.forEach(r=>{%><tr><td><%=r.id%></td><td><%=r.name%></td><td><%=r.status==='approved'?'승인':r.status==='rejected'?'반려':'대기'%></td><td><%=r.admin_memo||'-'%></td></tr><%})%></table></section></main></body></html>
